data.description:
The time is NOW!! Make a move on this lovely 3 bedroom, 1 bathroom home ready for its new owners!! Needing something MOVE-IN READY?! THIS IS IT!! Newer roof, windows, plumbing, and even foundation work preformed all within the past 15 months!! HVAC unit less than 3 years old, beautiful vinyl flooring, granite countertops in the kitchen including stainless steel appliances. What more could you ask for??

I almost forgot to mention the covered patio, private metal fence, and storage shed with electricity in the backyard!! The perfect canvas to start your backyard oasis! Come see this home today!! Photo staging applied to living area.
